[I] Documentation Utilities

[T] The purpose of the Docutils project is to create a set of tools for
[T] processing plaintext documentation into useful formats, such as HTML,
[T] XML, and LaTeX. Includes reStructuredText, the easy to read, easy to
[T] use, what-you-see-is-what-you-get plaintext markup language.

[U] https://docutils.sourceforge.net/

